sed, use cases: <a href=\"https://weclouddata.com/blog/cloud-computing-in-the-healthcare-industry/?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=saudi-healthcare\">link to blog</a></div><div><br /></div><div>Want me to send over a quick overview deck of we can help\u00a0<a href=\"https://weclouddata.com/corporate-training/?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=saudi-healthcare\">upskill</a> \u00a0{{companyName}} employees?</div><div><br /></div><div>Best,</div><div>WeCloudData</div>"}]}, {"type": "email", "delay": 1, "variants": [{"subject": "", "body": "<div>{{firstName}}\u00a0</div><div><br /></div><div>We built a healthcare-focused <a href=\"https://weclouddata.com/corporate-training/?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=saudi-healthcare\">AI upskilling program</a> to close that gap \u2014 designed for frontline workers, admins, and medical leaders. short sessions. localized content. real use cases.</div><div><br /></div><div>It\u2019s not about turning doctors into data scientists. It\u2019s about helping them make better decisions, faster.</div><div><br /></div><div>\u2014 Lets <a href=\"https://meetings.hubspot.com/warney/talk-to-wecloud-program-advisor?uuid=f772e830-c1fe-4c3a-af95-34b2bb557260&amp;utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=saudi-healthcare\">chat</a> next week?</div><div><br /></div><div>{{RANDOM | Best, | Regards, | Cheers,}}</div><div>WeCloudData</div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div>"}]}]}]', FALSE, '["louise.c@weclouddata.net", "louise.c@weclouddata.org", "louise.c@weclouddata.us", "louise.cheng@weclouddata.org", "louise.cheng@weclouddata.us", "louise@weclouddata.net", "louise@weclouddata.org", "louise@weclouddata.us", "louise_c@weclouddata.org", "louise_c@weclouddata.us"]', 300.0, 'true', '[]', TRUE, TRUE, 'false', 'f44277de-69b2-4bc3-a69c-28afd4094123', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL) ON CONFLICT (id) DO NOTHING;
