/div><div>We {{work with|partner with|assist}} financial institutions across the Kingdom to redefine digital customer experiences\u2014particularly around {{customer onboarding and data analytics|mobile app engagement and backend automation|secure payments and AI-driven personalization}}.</div><div><br /></div><div>Many banks we speak with are aligning their innovation roadmaps to Vision 2030\u2019s digital transformation goals\u2014but struggle with fragmented legacy systems, poor CX metrics, or under-leveraged data.</div><div><br /></div><div>{{Would you be open to a <a href=\"https://meetings.hubspot.com/warney/talk-to-wecloud-program-advisor?uuid=f772e830-c1fe-4c3a-af95-34b2bb557260&amp;utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=saudi-banking\">15-minute call</a> next week to explore whether this is relevant to {{companyName}}?|Happy to share more if improving CX and data use is a current priority.}}</div><div><br /></div><div>Best regards,\u00a0</div><div>WeCloudData</div>"}]}, {"type": "email", "delay": 2, "variants": [{"subject": "how {{companyName}} can keep fraud in check", "body": "<div>Hi {{firstName}}\u00a0</div><div><br /></div><div>Bank fraud is like a stubborn bug \u2013 it keeps changing and trying new tricks! I know many banks worry about scale &amp; accuracy. False alerts overwhelm teams, making it harder to detect what actually matters.</div><div><br /></div><div>Our <a href=\"https://weclouddata.com/blog/fraud-detection-in-the-banking-industry-leveraging-machine-learning-for-credit-card-fraud-detection/\">recent blog</a> walks through how AI and machine learning can detect anomalies in real time, reduce false positives, and help banks adapt faster than manually coded rules can ever keep up.\u00a0</div><div><br /></div><div>Could this kind of upskilling help {{companyName}} better support fraud or compliance teams?</div><div><br /></div><div>Regards,</div><div>WeCloudData</div>"}]}, {"type": "email", "delay": 1, "variants": [{"subject": "", "body": "<div>Hi {{firstName}}\u00a0</div><div><br /></div><div>Just checking that my email didn''t landed in spam, I know you might be busy but I believe we can help relive {{companyName}}''s manual burden.\u00a0</div><div><br /></div><div>We have successfully helped <a href=\"https://weclouddata.com/corporate-training/?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=saudi-banking\">upskill other banks</a> e.g. China Construction Bank, Scotiabank and more into learning &amp; applying tools in-house that are relevant to the banking industry.</div><div><br /></div><div>Want to have <a href=\"https://meetings.hubspot.com/warney/talk-to-wecloud-program-advisor?uuid=f772e830-c1fe-4c3a-af95-34b2bb557260&amp;utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=saudi-banking\">quick chat next week</a> of we can support {{companyName}} deploying AI?</div><div><br /></div><div>Best,</div><div>WeCloudData</div>"}]}, {"type": "email", "delay": 1, "variants": [{"subject": "", "body": "<div>Hey {{firstName}}\u00a0</div><div><br /></div><div>I know your schedule is crazy busy. I reached out a bit ago about how WeCloudData helps banks use <a href=\"https://weclouddata.com/corporate-training/?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=saudi-banking\">AI</a> to solve big problems \u2013 like speeding things up, making customers happier, or boosting security.</div><div><br /></div><div>No pressure at all, but even a quick <a href=\"https://meetings.hubspot.com/warney/talk-to-wecloud-program-advisor?uuid=f772e830-c1fe-4c3a-af95-34b2bb557260&amp;utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=saudi-banking\">10-minute chat</a> could spark an idea that makes a real difference for {{companyName}}.</div><div><br /></div><div>Best,</div><div>WeCloudData</div>"}]}]}]', FALSE, '["louise.c@weclouddata.org", "louise.c@weclouddata.net", "louise.c@weclouddata.us", "louise@weclouddata.org", "louise@weclouddata.us", "louise@weclouddata.net