014it can just make the day-to-day easier. Think:</div><div><br /></div><div>- Individuals getting 24/7 answers/scheduling meetings from chatbots (so your inbox doesn\u2019t explode) - Documents that sort and summarize themselves - Smarter planning with data you already have</div><div><br /></div><div>We\u2019ve helped other teams like Govt of Canada, Universities like Calgary to roll this out\u2014with\u00a0<a href=\"https://weclouddata.com/corporate-training/?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=uae-govt\">training that sticks</a>. Interested? Book<a href=\"https://meetings.hubspot.com/warney/talk-to-wecloud-program-advisor?uuid=f772e830-c1fe-4c3a-af95-34b2bb557260&amp;utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=uae-govt\">\u00a0HERE</a> for a quick chat.</div>"}, {"subject": "", "body": "<div>Hi {{firstName}} ,</div><div><br /></div><div>Gov orgs handle thousands of docs daily\u2014forms, contracts, reports. But most of it\u2019s unstructured, search barely works, and no one has time to read 100+ pages.</div><div><br /></div><div>We used AI to: Extract meaning from messy docs, auto-tag and group content and find what matters\u2014no exact keywords needed. Read our case study: <a href=\"https://weclouddata.com/blog/consulting/consulting-case-study-topic-modelling-on-technician-notes/\">HERE</a>.</div><div><br /></div><div>Imagine that across policy, legal, HR, procurement at {{companyName}}.</div><div>We help gov teams integrate tools like this and train staff to use them. Want to <a href=\"https://meetings.hubspot.com/warney/talk-to-wecloud-program-advisor?uuid=f772e830-c1fe-4c3a-af95-34b2bb557260&amp;utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=uae-govt\">chat</a> how it could work with your data?</div><div><br /></div><div>Best,</div><div>WeCloudData</div>"}]}, {"type": "email", "delay": 1, "variants": [{"subject": "", "body": "<div>{{firstName}} - I know this is a cold email, but I wanted to reach out because I genuinely believe we can help with your AI needs.</div><div><br /></div><div>For over 8 years, we\u2019ve worked with government teams, building strong AI skills through\u00a0<a href=\"https://weclouddata.com/corporate-training/?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=uae-govt\">tailored training.</a></div><div><br /></div><div>Our trainers have hands-on experience in AI, data science, and big data. We cover everything from the basics to advanced applications\u2014making sure your team gains practical skills that improve services and decisions.</div><div><br /></div><div>If you\u2019re open to it, I\u2019d be hop on a <a href=\"https://meetings.hubspot.com/warney/talk-to-wecloud-program-advisor?uuid=f772e830-c1fe-4c3a-af95-34b2bb557260&amp;utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=uae-govt\">quick call</a> how we\u2019ve helped other agencies and explore if it might be a fit for your team.\u00a0</div><div><br /></div><div>Best,</div><div>WeCloudData</div>"}]}, {"type": "email", "delay": 1, "variants": [{"subject": "", "body": "<div>{{firstName}}\u00a0</div><div><br /></div><div>I\u2019ve sent a couple of notes about how {{companyName}} could help use AI solutions to solve redundant problems &amp; <a href=\"https://weclouddata.com/corporate-training/?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=uae-govt\">upskilling your team</a> to run it.</div><div><br /></div><div>I know how busy things can get. If now\u2019s not the right moment, no problem at all. But if exploring AI is on your mind, even for a quick <a href=\"https://meetings.hubspot.com/warney/talk-to-wecloud-program-advisor?uuid=f772e830-c1fe-4c3a-af95-34b2bb557260&amp;utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=uae-govt\">10-minute chat</a> about how it fits with the UAE''s vision.\u00a0</div><div><br /></div><div>I''d be happy to connect.</div><div><br /></div><div>Kind Regards,</div><div>WeCloudData</div>"}]}]}]', FALSE, '["louise.c@