014flexible, customized, hands-on training that empowers educators to use, teach, and apply AI tools confidently.</div><div><br /></div><div>{{Want to see how the University of Calgary approached it?|Can share how we helped UCalgary upskill teams across departments.}}</div><div><br /></div><div>Open to a low-key <a href=\"https://meetings.hubspot.com/warney/talk-to-wecloud-program-advisor?uuid=f772e830-c1fe-4c3a-af95-34b2bb557260&amp;utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=uae-education\">10-minute chat</a>?</div><div><br /></div><div>Best,</div><div>WeCloudData</div>"}]}, {"type": "email", "delay": 1, "variants": [{"subject": "", "body": "<div>Hey {{firstName}}\u00a0</div><div><br /></div><div>Just following up in case this slipped by\u2014still happy to share how we\u2019re helping UAE educators personalize learning with AI and possibly could help {{companyName}}.</div><div><br /></div><div>Worth sending over a <a href=\"https://meetings.hubspot.com/warney/talk-to-wecloud-program-advisor?uuid=f772e830-c1fe-4c3a-af95-34b2bb557260&amp;utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=uae-education\">10 min slot</a> next week?</div><div><br /></div><div>Best,</div><div><a href=\"https://weclouddata.com/corporate-training/?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=uae-education\">WeCloudData</a></div>"}, {"subject": "", "body": "<div>Hey {{firstName}}\u00a0</div><div><br /></div><div>Not sure if this is on {{companyName}}''s radar right now\u2014but if exploring <a href=\"https://weclouddata.com/corporate-training/?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=uae-education\">AI solutions</a> is something your team might revisit soon, I\u2019d be glad to share a 2-minute walkthrough.</div><div><br /></div><div>If the timing\u2019s off, no worries at all\u2014we can <a href=\"https://meetings.hubspot.com/warney/talk-to-wecloud-program-advisor?uuid=f772e830-c1fe-4c3a-af95-34b2bb557260&amp;utm_source=newslette