rce=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=canada-finance-follow-up\" target=\"_blank\">AI Corproate Training</a>, a <strong>customized flexible</strong> solution to connect with industry experts to guide you.\u00a0</div><div><br /></div><div>Why should you join us? This is a perfect opportunity to use your <strong>company''s education funding\u00a0</strong>to upskill your team in AI <strong>without affecting your budget.</strong></div><div><br /></div><div>Warm Regards,</div><div><a href=\"https://weclouddata.com/corporate-training/?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=canada-finance-follow-uphttps://weclouddata.com/corporate-training/?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=canada-finance-follow-up\" target=\"_blank\">WeCloudData</a></div>"}, {"subject": "{{first_name}} thoughts?", "body": "<div>{{first_name}},</div><div><br /></div><div>Finance teams already using AI are seeing 30-50% efficiency gains\u2014from automating audits to predicting cash flow with 90%+ accuracy.</div><div><br /></div><div>But AI is only as good as the people using it. That''s where we come in. Our training helps finance teams automate tedious tasks\u2014like reconciliations and compliance reporting\u2014and spot risk-driving anomalies.</div><div><br /></div><div>Let\u2019s talk\u2014{{companyName}} could be running smarter, faster, and leaner in weeks. <a href=\"https://meetings.hubspot.com/warney/talk-to-wecloud-program-advisor?uuid=f772e830-c1fe-4c3a-af95-34b2bb557260&amp;utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=canada-finance-follow-up\" target=\"_blank\">Interested?</a></div><div><br /></div><div>Regards,</div><div><a href=\"https://weclouddata.com/corporate-training/?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=canada-finance-follow-uphttps://weclouddata.com/corporate-training/?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=canada-finance-follow-up\" target=\"_blank\">WeCloudData</a></div>"}]}, {"type": "email", "delay": 2, "variants": [{"subject": "", "body": "<div>{{firstName}} its me again,\u00a0</div><div><br /></div><div>I just read the KPMG report that shows 87% of Canadian companies are using AI in financial reporting\u2014yet 59% report a talent gap.\u00a0</div><div><br /></div><div>Although hiring new talent could solve this, you cannot rehire a whole team right?</div><div><br /></div><div>I\u2019d be happy to share some insights on effective upskilling training approaches if you\u2019re interested. Let me know if you\u2019d like to\u00a0<a href=\"https://meetings.hubspot.com/warney/talk-to-wecloud-program-advisor?uuid=f772e830-c1fe-4c3a-af95-34b2bb557260&amp;utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=canada-finance-follow-up\" target=\"_blank\">chat.</a></div><div><br /></div><div>Regards,</div><div><a href=\"https://weclouddata.com/corporate-training/?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=canada-finance-follow-uphttps://weclouddata.com/corporate-training/?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=canada-finance-follow-up\" target=\"_blank\">WeCloudData</a></div>"}, {"subject": "how CIBC scaled AI in finance", "body": "<div>{{first_name}},</div><div><br /></div><div>CIBC, a canadian company like {{companyName}}, struggled with slow, manual finance processes. after implementing AI, they:</div><ul data-start=\"2400\" data-end=\"2543\"><li data-start=\"2400\" data-end=\"2440\"><div>automated 75% of their reporting</div></li><li data-start=\"2441\" data-end=\"2478\"><div>cut forecasting errors by 40%</div></li><li data-start=\"2479\" data-end=\"2543\"><div>freed up their finance team for high-value strategy work</div></li></ul><div>The best part? it only took them a few weeks to get fully trained and running.</div><div><br /></div><div>Want to see how we can do it for you too?</div><div><br /></div><div>Best,</div><div><a href=\"https://weclouddata.com/corporate-training/?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=canada-finance-follow-uphttps://weclouddata.com/corporate-training/?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=canada-finance-follow-up\" target=\"_blank\">WeCloudData</a></div>"}]}, {"type": "email", "delay": 1, "variants": [{"subject": "", "body": "<div>{{firstName}}\u00a0</div><div><br /></div><div>Are manual reports and outdated risk methods slowing your team down\u2014or have you tried AI tools without real results? Running a one-man show can be overwhelming.\u00a0</div><div><br /></div><div>Our\u00a0<a href=\"https://weclouddata.com/corporate-training/?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=canada-finance-follow-uphttps://weclouddata.com/corporate-training/?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=canada-finance-follow-up\" target=\"_blank\">AI training</a> offers a sustainable solution to boost efficiency and drive growth.</div><div><br /></div><div>Interested in learning more?</div><div><br /></div><div>Best,</div><div>WeCloudData</div>"}]}]}]', FALSE, '["louise.c@weclouddata.org", "louise.c@weclouddata.us", "louise.cheng@weclouddata.org", "louise.c@weclouddata.net", "louise.cheng@weclouddata.us", "louise@weclouddata.org", "louise@weclouddata.us", "louise_c@weclouddata.org", "louise_c@weclouddata.us", "louise@weclouddata.net"]', 300.0, 'true', '[]', TRUE, TRUE, 'false', 'f44277de-69b2-4bc3-a69c-28afd4094123', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL) ON CONFLICT (id) DO NOTHING;
