ound by delaying AI adoption?</div><div>Many competitors are already using AI to speed up ops, cut costs, and build more resilient supply chains. Sticking to traditional tools while others automate can lead to slower response times\u2014and a growing skills gap.</div><div><br /></div><div>We help logistics leaders explore\u00a0<a href=\"https://weclouddata.com/corporate-training/?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=uae-logistics\">AI through hands-on training</a>and easy integration.</div><div><br /></div><div>Would you be open to a <a href=\"https://meetings.hubspot.com/warney/talk-to-wecloud-program-advisor?uuid=f772e830-c1fe-4c3a-af95-34b2bb557260&amp;utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=uae-logistics\">quick, informal chat</a> next Thursday about how AI could work for {{companyName}}? No pressure\u2014just a conversation.</div><div><br /></div><div>{{RANDOM | Best, | Regards, | Cheers,}}</div><div>WeCloudData</div>"}]}, {"type": "email", "delay": 2, "variants": [{"subject": "", "body": "<div>Hi {{firstName}},</div><div><br /></div><div>I was chatting with a freight forwarder recently who told me how much time they spend on repetitive tasks like requesting quotes and crunching numbers. It made me realize how AI could easily handle these\u2014automating quotes, analyzing shipments, tracking payments, and cutting errors.</div><div><br /></div><div>At WeCloudData, we train teams to use AI practically so they can start benefiting right away. If you\u2019re curious how we can use AI to integrate a similar solution to help {{companyName}} team, let\u2019s connect!</div><div><br /></div><div>{{RANDOM | Best, | Regards, | Cheers,}}</div><div>WeCloudData</div>"}]}, {"type": "email", "delay": 1, "variants": [{"subject": "", "body": "<div>{{firstName}} its me again,</div><div><br /></div><div>Thought our <a href=\"https://weclouddata.com/blog/consulting/consulting-case-study-topic-modelling-on-technician-notes/\">case study</a> might interest you\u2014shows how we built a real-time streaming pipeline that drastically improved operational visibility.</div><div><br /></div><div>Think about it \u2013 inefficient data flows can hinder real-time tracking accuracy or delay crucial predictive maintenance insights, leading to service issues or unexpected downtime. This directly impacts efficiency and customer satisfaction.</div><div><br /></div><div>Happy to talk if you''re exploring how to bring this in-house for {{companyName}}.</div><div><br /></div><div>Best,\u00a0</div><div>WeCloudData</div>"}]}, {"type": "email", "delay": 1, "variants": [{"subject": "", "body": "<div>Hi {{firstName}}</div><div><br /></div><div>I know you have a lot on your plate.</div><div><br /></div><div>If a quick, no-strings-attached chat about how <a href=\"https://weclouddata.com/corporate-training/?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=uae-logistics\">AI upskilling or integration</a> could support your team at {{companyName}} ever feels timely, just let me know. Or book a <a href=\"https://meetings.hubspot.com/warney/talk-to-wecloud-program-advisor?uuid=f772e830-c1fe-4c3a-af95-34b2bb557260&amp;utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=uae-logistics\">meeting</a> here for forseeable future.</div><div><br /></div><div>Cheers,</div><div>WeCloudData</div>"}]}]}]', FALSE, '["louise.c@weclouddata.org", "louise.c@weclouddata.us", "louise.cheng@weclouddata.org", "louise.c@weclouddata.net", "louise.cheng@weclouddata.us", "louise@weclouddata.us", "louise_c@weclouddata.org", "louise@weclouddata.org", "louise_c@weclouddata.us", "louise@weclouddata.net"]', 300.0, 'true', '[]', TRUE, TRUE, 'false', 'f44277de-69b2-4bc3-a69c-28afd4094123', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL) ON CONFLICT (id) DO NOTHING;
