variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre\"><div>there\u2019s pressure to do something before the board starts asking questions</div></li></ul><div><br /></div><div>We help mining &amp; oil teams in the UAE, no fluff. real use cases. <a href=\"https://weclouddata.com/corporate-training/?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=uae-resources\" target=\"_blank\">Real training</a>. <a href=\"https://meetings.hubspot.com/warney/talk-to-wecloud-program-advisor?uuid=f772e830-c1fe-4c3a-af95-34b2bb557260&amp;utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=uae--resources\" target=\"_blank\">Curious?</a></div><div><br /></div><div>Best,</div><div>WeCloudData</div>"}, {"subject": "{{companyName}} using AI like it should?", "body": "<div>{{firstName}},</div><div><br /></div><div>Imagine this\u2014{{companyName}} ops team spots a critical issue before it hits production. not because someone flagged it, but because AI did.</div><div><br /></div><div>Sounds futuristic, right? except it\u2019s not. Some of your UAE peers are already doing this\u2014cutting downtime, streamlining inspections, and automating the ugly reporting stuff.</div><div><br /></div><div>We help teams actually get there\u2014fast, without the AI chaos.</div><div>Want a peek at how it works?</div><div><br /></div><div>Best Regards,</div><div><a href=\"https://weclouddata.com/corporate-training/?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=uae-resources\" target=\"_blank\">WeCloudData</a></div>"}]}, {"type": "email", "delay": 2, "variants": [{"subject": "", "body": "<div>{{firstName}},\u00a0</div><div><br /></div><div>According to a recent BCG report, 85% of energy leaders see AI as a top priority\u2014but only 21% have an internal roadmap to adopt it effectively.</div><div><br /></div><div>We help mining &amp; oil leaders in the UAE close that gap\u2014fast.</div><div>Curious where {{companyName}} stands?</div><div><br /></div><div>B